{"tha-ap196:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap196:0.2":"Tamalapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap196:0.3":"Asokapujakattheraapadana ","tha-ap196:1.1":"“Tivarayam pure ramme, ","tha-ap196:1.2":"rajuyyanam ahu tada; ","tha-ap196:1.3":"Uyyanapalo tatthasim, ","tha-ap196:1.4":"ranno baddhacaro aham. ","tha-ap196:2.1":"Padumo nama namena, ","tha-ap196:2.2":"sayambhu sappabho ahu; ","tha-ap196:2.3":"Nisinnam pundarikamhi, ","tha-ap196:2.4":"chaya na jahi tam munim. ","tha-ap196:3.1":"Asokam pupphitam disva, ","tha-ap196:3.2":"pindibharam sudassanam; ","tha-ap196:3.3":"Buddhassa abhiropesim, ","tha-ap196:3.4":"jalajuttamanamino. ","tha-ap196:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap196:4.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap196:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap196:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap196:5.1":"Sattatimsamhito kappe, ","tha-ap196:5.2":"solasa arananjaha; ","tha-ap196:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanna, ","tha-ap196:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap196:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap196:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap196:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap196:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma asokapujako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap196:8.1":"Asokapujakattherassapadanam catuttham. "}